.SH BUGS
.IP \(bu 2
The \fBinclude/\fP directory is always created empty; files must be added manually before compilation.
.IP \(bu
Concurrent operations on the same project directory are not serialised; while individual writes are atomic, the overall state may be inconsistent if multiple processes write simultaneously.
.IP \(bu
No cryptographic signatures yet; integrity relies solely on SHA-512 hashes.
.IP \(bu
The \fBChmod\fP step is not supported on non-Unix platforms and will return an error.
